'''[[Cesta/Legends|Cesta]] security droids''' were class-five personal [[Security droid/Legends|security droids]] made by [[Cestus Cybernetics]]. They were its most famous product prior to the release of the [[JK-13]]. Cesta [[Droid/Legends|droids]] used [[Gabonna memory crystal]]s.

At the start of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], Cestus Cybernetics was unable to finish its large order for the Cestas due to the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] restricting use of the Gabonnas.

